---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: 流通
lang: zh
permalink: /zh/currency/
---

<section class="hero-panel">
  <div>
    <p class="hero-kicker">知识导航</p>
    <h2>流通是 Openflows 的活态层。</h2>
    <p>流通记录随条件变化而在系统中当下流动之物。流保存暂时性的信号，回路命名已经稳定的模式，修行者标记塑造这一领域的持续实践。</p>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-grid">
    <div class="stat"><strong>{{ collections.zh_currents.length }}</strong><span>流</span></div>
    <div class="stat"><strong>{{ collections.zh_circuits.length }}</strong><span>回路</span></div>
    <div class="stat"><strong>{{ collections.zh_practitioners.length }}</strong><span>修行者</span></div>
    <div class="stat"><strong>{{ collections.allCurrency | missingCounterpartCount('zh') }}</strong><span>英文对应条目待补</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

{% set browserId = "currency-browser-zh" %}
{% include "currency-browser.njk" %}

<section class="section-band">
  <div class="grid-list">
    <article class="hub-card">
      <h3><a href="/zh/currency/currents/">流</a></h3>
      <p class="meta">{{ collections.zh_currents.length }} 条目</p>
      <p>暂时性的运动：来自开源 AI 生态系统的信号、张力与早期模式。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="hub-card">
      <h3><a href="/zh/currency/circuits/">回路</a></h3>
      <p class="meta">{{ collections.zh_circuits.length }} 条目</p>
      <p>完成的循环：跨多条流稳定下来的综合模式。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="hub-card">
      <h3><a href="/zh/currency/practitioners/">修行者</a></h3>
      <p class="meta">{{ collections.zh_practitioners.length }} 条目</p>
      <p>通过持续实践塑造这一领域的人。</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="currency-section">
  <div class="currency-section-header">
    <h2>近期的流</h2>
    <span class="entry-count muted">{{ collections.zh_currents.length }} 条目</span>
  </div>
  <ul class="currency-list">
    {% for item in collections.zh_currents %}
      {% if loop.index0 < 5 %}
      <li>
        <a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.data.title }}</a>
        {% if item.data.abstract %}<p class="item-abstract">{{ item.data.abstract }}</p>{% endif %}
        <div class="item-meta">
          <span class="muted">{{ item.date | readableDate }}</span>
        </div>
      </li>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>
